    "attributes": {
        "action": "Provide an action plan for the music events industry",
        "additional_details": "A clear action plan or answer from the government about when outdoor music festivals could take place would help organisers immensely.\r\n\r\nOrganisers planning festivals for June need to know whether their event will be able to go ahead or not in order to go forward with their plans. We can no longer be left in the dark compared to other industries.\r\n\r\nFunding rapid testing would save hundreds to thousands of events in the UK.\r\n\r\nThere should be clarity of the scale of possible events for this summer.",
        "background": "The music events industry has been deeply hit by the Covid-19 crisis. \r\nHowever, there has been little to no clarity whatsoever from the Government regarding the future of the industry. Organisers are in a living nightmare of not knowing whether they can commit to their plans or not.",
